Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F08\u002Fjquery-why-it-declined\u002F","jQuery Was Once King — So Why Did It Fall Off?","2025-12-08 21:35:24","7",{"url":763,"title":764,"date":765,"readingMinutes":766},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F05\u002Fjavascript-generator-functions\u002F","What Are JavaScript Generator Functions (function*)? The Function You Can Pause and Resume","2025-12-05 13:40:31","5",1784011702208]